{"tid":1104582,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚浸溫泉，兄弟又話我碌鳩短小......明明我只係扯咗一半","createTime":"2019-04-13T08:46:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T01:06:25.000Z","uid":238361,"like":1,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0460b5f09f44cd2a804f62a0829eec74cf55b1fa","tid":1104582,"uid":238361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T08:46:04.000Z","msg":"話說琴晚又喺京都浸溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行過女湯，見到個大波㗎妹，心生淫慾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n弟弟唔覺意扯咗少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為有啲大，所以條毛巾都包唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而佢地唔知係咪未見過大波妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扯到衡一衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地已經硬到條毛巾壓唔低條撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由此可見，佢地已經發揮咗近乎100%嘅實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而我就覺得條女一般貨色<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以弟弟都好有保留<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知佢地就話我短小<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地扯到衡都只係比我扯到一半大少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n憑咩笑我短<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我扯到衡，頂到入你地大腸喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本就係你地食開屎，先咁敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後就懶得戚，以為自己好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地點扯都唔夠我粗大就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我呢啲叫做大丈夫能屈能伸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地唔識嘢就唔好亂咁評論我碌鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相信連登仔應該識啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想問下，有冇人同我一樣，扯旗會分好多種唔同階段架，就好似手機差電咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n70%!! <br />\n80%!!~!~!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n100%!!!!!!~!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d401c1e467172283325e40fafa7af7d0a9feba5f","tid":1104582,"uid":79471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T08:47:05.000Z","msg":"你要畀佢哋感受下<br />\n鳩講冇用 要鳩插"},{"pid":"c4f2a148998c4aaf98e1fc4654de158f6a74d49f","tid":1104582,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T08:50:34.000Z","msg":"樓豬納米鳩"},{"pid":"8062ad7bcafd4f148a0315d05c8f349e2a5458a3","tid":1104582,"uid":238361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4f2a148998c4aaf98e1fc4654de158f6a74d49f","tid":1104582,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T08:50:34.000Z","msg":"樓豬納米鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T08:52:30.000Z","msg":"正文唔記得利申返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自問碌鳩中上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6d3d35b39daba4722019d3796a4d4a2ad48b97","tid":1104582,"uid":238361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d401c1e467172283325e40fafa7af7d0a9feba5f","tid":1104582,"uid":79471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T08:47:05.000Z","msg":"你要畀佢哋感受下<br />\n鳩講冇用 要鳩插"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T08:54:50.000Z","msg":"非gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有女咁話我嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我頂到入一入，屌到佢喊喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab06730b94181043d4b5f91ee0e13d48c4fc433","tid":110